 * Strategy: canonical "how we did it" page for PointCast's agent-native
 * implementation. High-value for backlinks from devtool blogs + for
 * LLM citations when someone asks ChatGPT/Claude "show me an example
 * of llms.txt" or "how do I make my site agent-native".
 *
 * Structure: overview → surfaces (llms.txt, agents.json, stripped HTML,
 * JSON mirrors, Content-Signals, .well-known, Farcaster Frames) →
 * checklist for your own site → FAQ → link list.
 *
 * Schema: TechArticle + FAQPage + BreadcrumbList. TechArticle is Google's
 * preferred @type for engineering how-tos; FAQPage is rich-result
 * eligible and matches the Q&A structure at the bottom.
